FLOW SUMMARY
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  Doctor opens DoctorAppointmentsPage
    → clicks "Complete & Prescribe" on a confirmed/pending appointment
    → navigates to /appointments/:id/prescribe

  PrescriptionFormPage loads the appointment details
    → doctor fills Clinical Notes, Medicines table, Lab Tests,
       Advice, Follow-up date
    → clicks "Complete & Generate PDF"

  POST /appointments/:id/prescribe/   (PrescribeAppointmentView)
    1. Validates doctor owns the appointment
    2. Inserts prescriptions row (doc_create_prescription)
       — also marks appointment status = 'completed'
    3. Inserts each medicine row (doc_add_prescription_medicine)
    4. Calls generate_prescription_pdf() → ReportLab builds PDF
       saved to  media/prescriptions/<doctor_id>/<rx_number>_<id8>.pdf
    5. Updates pdf_path on the prescription row
    6. Returns full prescription + pdf_url

  Frontend opens PDF in new tab, then redirects back to appointments.

  Patient can view their prescription PDF from:
    GET /prescriptions/my/   → list with pdf_url links
